STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Rafael RODRIGUEZ, a/k/a Peter Rodriguez, Defendant-Respondent. C-1008 September Term 2016
079235 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001078-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is dismissed. See Order on M-1533-16.
